name: NAPD 2
notes: Chron uses Ambrosia rise (100±50) at 30 cm and Tsuga decline (4800±200) at 670 cm. C14 date at 990 cm (10,030±150) appears OK, but C14 date at 670 cm (5800±105) appears ca. 1000 yr too old. Basal age of 12,000±500 based on Dyke and Prest (1987) map.
